        "content": "## Workflow B — Campaign Surge Webhook\n\n**Trigger:** POST /webhook/surge\n\n**Purpose:** Immediately dispatches a surge test across all 6 regions when called. Used by the dashboard 'Trigger surge' button and callable externally during live campaigns.\n\n**Flow:**\nWebhook (POST /surge) → Dispatch GitHub Action (surge mode, all 6 regions) → Respond { triggered: true }\n\n**What surge mode does:** Fires 20 concurrent requests per region (120 total across all regions) to simulate a campaign traffic spike — tests whether the target URL stays available under high concurrent load.\n\n**Direct call:** POST https://n8n-j39n.sliplane.app/webhook/surge\n\n**Dashboard path:** Control page → Trigger surge button → Cloudflare Worker /api/trigger → GitHub Actions workflow_dispatch"
